<p><strong>13. Businesses with complete profiles are 70% more likely to attract store visits.</strong>
Source: Google
Google rewards completeness. A fully filled-out profile directly translates to foot traffic.</p>
<p><strong>14. Customers are 2.7x more likely to trust a business with a complete GBP.</strong>
Source: Google
Trust drives conversions. A complete profile signals legitimacy to consumers comparing options.</p>
<p><strong>15. 86% of GBP views come from discovery searches, not direct.</strong>
Source: Birdeye, 2025
