<p><strong>16. GBP profiles with photos get 42% more direction requests.</strong>
Source: Google
Photos drive action. Businesses that upload quality images see measurably more visits.</p>
<p><strong>17. 71% of GBP interactions come from mobile devices.</strong>
Source: Search Endurance, 2025
