<h2>Online Reviews and Trust Statistics</h2>
<p>Reviews are the new word of mouth. BrightLocal's 2026 Local Consumer Review Survey shows consumer expectations rising fast.</p>
<p><strong>19. 97% of consumers read reviews for local businesses.</strong>
