<p><strong>27. Google review share dropped from 83% to 71% between 2025 and 2026.</strong>
Source: BrightLocal LCRS, 2026
Google still leads but its dominance is slipping. Apple Maps, ChatGPT, and niche platforms are gaining ground.</p>
<p><strong>28. Displaying reviews increases conversion rates by up to 270%.</strong>
Source: Spiegel Research Center
